WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:10.540
 In June 2014, Johnson Controls opened its latest customer and education center in Aarhus, Denmark's second largest city. 

00:00:10.560 --> 00:00:17.200
 The Customer Center is located at the Johnson Controls - Sabroe factory and its administration building. 

00:00:17.200 --> 00:00:24.040
 The 1000m2 customer center is part of a plant specializing in industrial cooling. 

00:00:24.170 --> 00:00:30.560
 The Customer Center focuses on the latest trends in industrial cooling 

00:00:30.560 --> 00:00:42.220
 Our employees, customers, partners and consultants have a unique opportunity not only to learn more about new products, but also to test them directly. 

00:00:42.320 --> 00:00:47.059
 The 700m2 showroom is the heart of the customer center. 

00:00:47.059 --> 00:00:59.230
 Here, visitors can view products and solutions for different business areas. 

00:00:59.230 --> 00:01:08.590
 No matter if you go to the aviation, food, data center or medical facilities, we have the technology and knowledge you need. 

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:16.640
 We offer you the opportunity to organize a product presentation, seminar, conference or testing in our center. 

00:01:16.800 --> 00:01:27.920
 Our showroom is fully equipped with products and audiovisual equipment. We are able to adapt everything to your requirements. 

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:30.880
 In the workshop area of ​​200m2 we provide 

00:01:30.920 --> 00:01:44.710
 training Johnson Controls engineers, customers and partners across Europe using real-world solutions and situations. We will improve the knowledge and capabilities of our customers and employees. 

00:01:44.710 --> 00:01:53.020
 There are also 2 conference rooms equipped with the necessary facilities in the center 

00:01:53.020 --> 00:01:59.340
 such as a video conferencing facility for virtual training and meetings. 

00:01:59.340 --> 00:02:06.780
 We invite you to visit our customer center. You will have the opportunity to learn more about the latest innovations and see them on the spot. 

00:02:06.780 --> 00:02:17.600
 Find out how you can work with us to help improve the efficiency of your buildings and industrial locations. 

